    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Project Utgardr is a first-person parkour platform adventure inspired by Norse and pre-Viking culture.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adventuring amidst the mountains of her homeland, Thyra finds a fissure that mysteriously appeared on a cliff face and a hidden passage that crumbles behind her as she passes through it. <br>Thyra, now trapped in uncharted territory and searching for a way home, quickly gets her bearings in the arduous environment using her climbing abilities, discovering timeworn engravings and weathered altars. <br>Coming across an ancient, forgotten tale, Thyra discovers her role in it and follows its fragments to reveal its secret.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878290/extras/bf2119e463d3ae60e8e8f8d681c9c702.poster.avif?t=1736450648\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878290/extras/bf2119e463d3ae60e8e8f8d681c9c702.webm?t=1736450648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878290/extras/bf2119e463d3ae60e8e8f8d681c9c702.mp4?t=1736450648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ᚱ - The Unexpected Journey of a Young Norse Woman</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore breathtaking landscapes and perilous precipices on a homeward journey after being suddenly stranded in a forgotten corner of ancient Scandinavia.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ᚱ - Intuitive Parkour and Platforming</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take advantage of Thyra’s parkour abilities to traverse the crumbling road. Sprint through various environments and overcome different obstacles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ᚱ - Flashes of Norse Culture</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The ancient runes carved on the hidden crags point towards the right path and abandoned shrines built by an old Norse civilization centuries ago.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ᚱ - Unseen Forces Guide You</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow shards of a lost myth chiseled into the face of the mountain and discover its secret. Locate strange glowing flowers and pray to the Horgr scattered all over for a safe haven. Something seems keen to help you on this journey…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878290/extras/4d62d6a8450891cf924d409472381eda.poster.avif?t=1736450648\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878290/extras/4d62d6a8450891cf924d409472381eda.webm?t=1736450648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878290/extras/4d62d6a8450891cf924d409472381eda.mp4?t=1736450648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
